Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术是将物质理解分解并且再构筑的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不是万能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不能从无中诞生物质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须付出相应的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就是炼金术的基本 等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师有一个禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是任何人都不能触犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德他们遇到的男人——马可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有一个不完整的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被爱德的诚心所感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可说出了隐藏研究资料的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修理完机械铠的爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了有马可研究资料的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国立中央图书馆第一分馆前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可的研究资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太麻烦了 所以把整个建筑都烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央市都做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我刚刚说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢之小弟发现马可的资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边已经搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以回来看看东方之都的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库拉托尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有味道 有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着血之味道的伊修瓦尔人就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把那家伙吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃得不剩一根头发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}被隐藏的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从艾尔利克兄弟的事件以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有人提供斯卡的情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是已经不在东方之都了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也得让他在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能把中央市没处理好的事件解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这支股票也就涨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能利用的东西全都利用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我爬到大总统的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握了全部军事权为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意一下不妥的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽量注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才传来了马鲁河发生爆炸的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煤气爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近比较乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是斯卡穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的出血状况这么严重 应该不会安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 直到确认他死亡为止都不能放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈博克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带领你的部队去清理那些瓦砾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要日以继夜进行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要把那家伙的尸体找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我们过劳死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不亲眼见到那家伙的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不能安心约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 下次再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过搞得他那副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡一时半会也动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再回趟中央市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把斯卡的事情报告给父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧得一点都不剩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是罗斯少尉和普罗修军曹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部要求你出席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克的护卫由我们接手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 本想总算能和闷热的大叔说拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是护卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于图书馆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人对于第一分馆的资料非常精通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 已经离职了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉没法期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐突地问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么总是穿着铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉 这是什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 好漂亮的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这书山是什 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有人住着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人被埋进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快挖 快挖 快挖 快挖这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心把书山弄塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为就这么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是谢丝卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾在第一分馆的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一分馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么美妙的发音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从出生就喜欢书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我决定在那里就职的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是升天一般的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 忘记是在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是看书导致被解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让生病的妈妈进入更好的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本应该好好工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了读书以外干什么都很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里都找不到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我是废人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社会的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想打听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是否知道提姆·马可写的研究书在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提姆·马可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提姆·马可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是手写的 而且还乱七八糟地插进了分类不同的书架里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 果然是被完全烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想读那本研究书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是被烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书的内容我全都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个 所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对读过一次的书里面的内容全都会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点花时间 要全部抄出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提姆·马可写的研究书之手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为量有点多 所以花了5天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界上还有这么厉害的人呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是马可的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提姆·马可着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日的一千种菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂糖一大勺 加水少量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是今日的一千种菜谱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 这哪里是重要文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是照着记忆里面的全抄下来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来完全是白跑了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和马可写的一字一句都完全一样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 带上这些回中央图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在那里的话 相关书籍也都很齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 谢礼 谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的登录号码和证明身份的银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我的年度研究费里取出那些交给谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去大总统府的国家炼金术师机关就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡 真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从研究费…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么金额
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一出手就是这个金额
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这料理书真的是炼金术的研究书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术被恶意使用的话可是危险的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用暗号来书写研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使一般人看起来只是普通的料理研究
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的内容只有写的人才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本非常难懂的炼金术书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么解读？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知识和灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就是靠毅力来钻研
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了就要晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 有鸽子料理的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可能说的就是绿色的狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲学家的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉梅露的古老手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者拉姆斯普林姆克写的有关贤者之石的书拿来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 让我们开始干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西 这该死的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 也许直接去问马可先生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去问了就是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲转移到优秀的医院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解读有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 多亏了你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个废人也能给别人带来帮助让我感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是废人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能对什么事情全心全意这本身就是一种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你有很强的记忆力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出自信来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从阿姆斯壮少佐那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我不是说了你到中央市的话先来跟我打声招呼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有急事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个休斯中佐在拉家常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个孩子到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近事件什么的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔克的合成兽事件还没有了结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你想起痛苦的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就已经是很忙的时期了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一分馆又全烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一分馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的书库里保管着事件的记录什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影响到业务真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人在找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实也读过军队的刑事记录 也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里工资不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拿出自信努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 马上工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大叔是人贩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能对什么事情全心全意这本身就是一种才能吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真能说呢 弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着某处的某位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从心底这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个某处的某位就继续全心全意地努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到闭馆时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到今天就整整十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真能集中精神一直到闭馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算解不开也不用自暴自弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了 暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得没错 这是恶魔的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会恨你的 马可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石的材料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了精制一个石头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要大量的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队在进行那种不人道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事能保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟今天也关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 饭也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是积累了疲劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近精神太过集中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦解读的资料内容是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也仅是回想起来就感觉全身不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃口饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了手能碰到的地方却被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却被抓住的东西踢飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来神是彻底地讨厌触犯禁忌的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生都会这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事一直想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为太害怕而没说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟 在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石居然隐藏了这种秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那种闷热的男人逼问的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到军队干了那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相有时确实残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可说的话 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能看到真相中的另一个真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相中的另一个真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和炼金术的研究书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面看到的只是真相的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 政府关联的炼金术研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央市里有四处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中马可氏所属的是第三研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里最可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市内的研究所我全部都看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好像没有什么重大研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个建筑是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有塌方的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么根据？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边就是监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石的材料是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监狱里也有死刑犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对外是说处刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…囚犯是材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摆出那种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不愿意那样想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系到管辖不同的监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说政府也脱不了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉是要调查到不得了的事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 让你们当作没听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许会成为高度的政治问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前 你们对这件事不要多问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟也要乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们是准备潜入这个建筑物调查内部吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想 没想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未使用的建筑却配门卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会因为炼成反应的光被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也封锁得严严实实的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那巨大的身体没法通过这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是喜欢才变这么大身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}（失落）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,66
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 48
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知死活的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像的还要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方如果是普通人的体型是无法通过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体小真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己说自己小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么现在没有使用呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有对剑保有荣耀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有明白自己属于异端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的住民们在狂笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血的刀刃在咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.86,0:24:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第8话 第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗中追求快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生死极限中感受生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报上你们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:42.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:58.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:05.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在逃避什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:35.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:39.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:43.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:49.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:33.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:38.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:44.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:02.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:12.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:29.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:34.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:40.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:45.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:51.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:55.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发
